b'Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) waa enzyme ku dhegan dusha sare ee unugyada (xidhmooyinka unugyada) ee sanbabada, wadnaha, kelyaha, iyo mindhicirka.
ACE2 waxay leedahay waxqabad ka soo horjeeda angiotensin-converting enzyme (ACE), iyadoo hoos u dhigeysa tirada angiotensin-II iyo kor u qaadida Angiotensin (1-7), taas oo ka dhigaysa bartilmaameed daawo oo rajo leh oo lagu daaweynayo cudurada wadnaha.
ACE2 ee bini'aadamka waxaa badanaa loo yaqaan hACE2.
Enzyme-ka beddelaya angiotensin 2 waa zinc-ka ku jira metaloenzyme-ka ku yaal dusha sare ee unugyada endothelial iyo unugyada kale.
ACE2 waxay leedahay domain-ka N-terminal M2 peptidase iyo domain-ka C-terminal renal amino acid transporter collectrin.
ACE2 waa borotiinka hal-ku-dhigga ah ee nooca I, oo leh domain firfircoon oo enzymatic ah oo lagu soo bandhigo dusha unugyada sanbabada iyo unugyada kale.
Xogta ACE2 ee xayawaanka ayaa laga soo saaraa xayawaanka xayawaanka ee xayawaanka ee ay leedahay enzymes kale oo loo yaqaan sheddase, iyo borotiinka la kala saaray ee la soo saaray ayaa loo sii daayaa dhiigga, ugu dambeynna waxaa lagu saaraa kaadida.
ACE2 waxaa lagu helaa xubnaha badankood: ACE2 waxay ku dhegan tahay unugyada unugyada, gaar ahaan unugyada nooca II ee sanbabada, unugyada xiidmaha yaryar, unugyada xididdada wadnaha iyo xididdada, iyo unugyada muruqyada fudud ee wadnaha ee xubnaha badankood.
Muuqaalka mRNA ee ACE2 waxaa sidoo kale laga helaa qalfoofka maskaxda, striatum, hypothalamus, iyo jirka.
Waxqabadka ugu weyn ee ACE2 waa in ay noqoto dheelitirka ACE.
ACE waxay u kala jeexdaa hormoonka angiotensin I ee loo yaqaan 'angiotensin II' ee ah hormoonka 'vasoconstrictive angiotensin II'.
Ugu dambeyntii, ACE2 waxay ka jartaa amino acid-ka phenylalanine ee terminal-ka ah ee angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) waxayna u biyo-dhaliyaan angiotensin (1-7) oo ah vasodilator (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 waxay sidoo kale kala jebin kartaa tiro kale oo ka mid ah peptides-ka [des-Arg9]-bradikinin, apelin, neurotensin, dinorphine A, iyo ghrelin.
ACE2 waxay sidoo kale xakameysaa gaadiidka xuubka ee gaadiidka amino acid-ka dhexdhexaadka ah ee SLC6A19 waxayna ku lug leedahay cudurka Hartnup.
Sida borotiinka transmembrane, ACE2 wuxuu u shaqeeyaa sidii barta ugu weyn ee lagu galo unugyada qaar ka mid ah cudurrada coronavirus, oo ay ku jiraan HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (viruska sababa SARS); iyo SARS-CoV-2 (viruska sababa COVID-19).
Si gaar ah, isku xirnaanta borotiinka S1 ee SARS-CoV iyo SARS-CoV2 ee la yiraahdo spike ama bulb ee ACE2 ee heerka unugyada ayaa keena endocytosis iyo wareejinta fayraska iyo enzymes-ka ee unugyada gudaha.
Nidaamkan gelitaanka fayraska ayaa sidoo kale u baahan in borotiinka S uu ku soo bilowdo serine protease TMPRSS2 ee martida ah, taas oo xannibaadeeda hadda la baarayayo daaweyn suurtagal ah.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, bulshooyinka xirfadeed iyo hay'adaha sharciyeynta badankood waxay kugula talinayaan in la sii wado daaweynta ACE inhibitor iyo ARB caadiga ah.
Dib u eegis nidaamsan iyo falanqayn, oo la daabacay July 11, 2012, ayaa lagu ogaaday in "isticmaalka ACE inhibitors ay keento hoos u dhac weyn oo 34% ah khatarta sambabada marka loo eego kontaroolada".
Intaa waxaa dheer, "isticmaalka ACE inhibitors ayaa sidoo kale hoos u dhigay halista cudurka sambabada ee bukaanka halista ugu weyn ee sambabada, gaar ahaan bukaanka qaba cudurka istaroogga iyo wadnaha oo aan shaqeyn.
Isticmaalka ACE inhibitors ayaa sidoo kale la xiriira dhimashada dhimashada ee cudurka sambabada, inkastoo natiijooyinka ay ka yar yihiin kan cudurka sambabada guud ahaan".
ACE2 ee bini'aadamka ee isku dhafan (rhACE2) ayaa la filayaa inay noqoto daaweyn cusub oo loogu talagalay dhaawaca sambabada ee daran, waxayna u muuqataa inay kordhineyso hemodynamics-ka sambabada iyo cusbooneysiinta oksijiinta ee doofaarka leh cudurka neefta ee loo yaqaan 'lipoplysarid-induced acute respiratory syndrome'.
Noloshu waxay ku egtahay 10 saacadood, bilowga shaqada 30 daqiiqo, iyo in ka badan 24 saacadood.
Qaar ka mid ah natiijooyinka ayaa muujinaya in rhACE2 ay noqon karto daawo rajo leh oo loogu talagalay bukaanka aan u dulqaadan karin nidaamka renin-angiotensin inhibitor (RAS inhibitor) ama cudurada leh angiotensin II ee wareegga dhiigga oo kordhay.
b'Barnaamijka COVID-19 waa barnaamij barnaamijyo ah oo loogu talagalay in lagu caawiyo raadraaca xiriirka ee ka hortagga cudurka faafa ee coronavirus ee 2019-2020, taas oo ah habka lagu aqoonsado dadka ("xidhiidhada") ee laga yaabo inay la xiriiraan dadka qaba cudurka.
