Bishii Abriil 10, 2020, Google iyo Apple waxay wada-shaqeyn ku dhawaaqeen inay ku darayaan shaqeynta si ay u taageeraan barnaamijyada ku saleysan Bluetooth si toos ah nidaamyada hawlgalka Android iyo iOS.
