Ilaa 14ka Abriil 2020, barnaamijku wuxuu weli sugaya ogolaanshaha dukaamada Google Play iyo Apple App Store.
12-kii Abriil, dowladdu waxay sheegtay in barnaamijka raadraaca xiriirka uu ku jiro marxaladda horumarinta oo ay diyaar u noqon doonto in la faafiyo toddobaadyo gudahood.
Australia iyo New Zealand ayaa ka fiirsanaya barnaamijyo ku saleysan barnaamijka TraceTogether ee Singapore iyo borotokoolka BlueTrace. Ruushka ayaa doonaya inuu soo bandhigo barnaamijyo loo yaqaan 'geofencing' oo loogu talagalay bukaannada laga helay COVID-19 ee ku nool Moscow; barnaamijkan waxaa loogu talagalay in lagu hubiyo inaysan ka bixin guryahooda.
Ross Anderson, oo ah borofisar ku takhasusay injineernimada amniga ee jaamacadda Cambridge, ayaa tilmaamay dhibaatooyin badan oo ku saabsan nidaamyada ku saleysan codsiyada, oo ay ka mid yihiin natiijooyinka been abuurka ah iyo suurtagalnimada in ay ka yaraadaan waxtarka haddii xogta ay codsigu soo qaato ay ku kooban tahay tiro yar oo dad ah.
Si looga hortago walaaca ku saabsan faafitaanka barnaamijyada khalkhal gelisa ama khatarta leh ee "coronavirus", Apple waxay xaddiday noocyada ururada ay ku dari karaan barnaamijyada la xiriira coronavirus App Store, taas oo ah in ay ku xaddidaan kaliya ururada "rasmiga ah" ama kuwa sumcad leh.
