Tallaabooyinka ka hortagga waa in la qaataa si loo yareeyo halista fayraska, gaar ahaan marka la sameeyo nidaamyada daryeelka caafimaadka ee soo saara aerosol, sida intubation ama hawo-qaadista gacanta.
Shaqaalaha caafimaadka ee daryeela bukaanka COVID-19, CDC waxay ku talineysaa in qofka la dhigo qolka go'doominta cudurka faafa ee hawada (AIIR) marka lagu daro isticmaalka taxaddarrada caadiga ah, tallaabooyinka ka hortagga xiriirka, iyo tallaabooyinka ka hortagga cudurka faafa. CDC waxay qeexaysaa tilmaamaha isticmaalka qalabka ilaalinta shaqsiyeed (APD) inta lagu jiro aafada.
Qalabka lagu taliyey waa: dharka APD, neefsashada ama maaskaro wajiga, indho ilaalinta, iyo galoofyada caafimaadka.
